title: Updates to work with newer versions of Android, some feature changes.

title: Fixed a number of bugs, updated to work with Droid.
message: Fixed a number of bugs, updated to work with Droid.

title: Changed icons to better follow the Android guidelines, made input handling more…
message: Changed icons to better follow the Android guidelines, made input handling more robust, especially for software keyboards. Got rid of media volume manipulation and pre-amplified sound file instead.

title: Used a single bell sound with repeats to replace multiple, larger sound files.…
message: Used a single bell sound with repeats to replace multiple, larger sound files. Amplified bell sound.

title: Forced media volume to max during bell sounds.
message: Forced media volume to max during bell sounds.

title: Updated to Cupcake (1.5) API, fixed bug on screen rotation, set vibrate mode to…
message: Updated to Cupcake (1.5) API, fixed bug on screen rotation, set vibrate mode to use vibration for alerts (in addition to setting the ringer mode to vibrate, which it already did).

title: Updated icon.

Updated icon.

title: Added icons, both original files and the properly-sized drawables, for the…
message:
Added icons, both original files and the properly-sized drawables, for the settings and about menus.
The icons were added to the menu layout xml file.
The about screen was updated to be scrollable, and the about text was reformatted.

title: Added copyright notices and GPL.
message:
Added copyright notices and GPL.
Added preferences for airplane mode, silent ringer mode, and keeping the screen on.
Added an about screen.
Added checking of input values and warnings to the user if invalid values are used.
